*.bag
# NOTE: a blanket "dataset_yolo/" ignore would also block
# dataset_yolo/README_YOLO_FORMAT.md from ever being tracked (git cannot
# re-include a file whose parent directory is fully excluded). These two
# patterns keep the same intent (never track the heavy images/labels) while
# still allowing the format README.
dataset_yolo/train/
dataset_yolo/val/
dataset_yolo/*.cache
bags/*.bag
*.zip
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.pt
*.onnx
*.torchscript
*.engine
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
